" ===========================
" Window Mappings
" ===========================

nnoremap <silent> <Space>w/ :vsplit<CR>
nnoremap <silent> <Space>w- :split<CR>

" Switch to last buffer used
nnoremap <silent> <Space><Tab> :b#<CR>

" Sensible buffer movement
map <C-H> <C-W>h
map <C-J> <C-W>j
map <C-K> <C-W>k
map <C-L> <C-W>l
